20:46.972 --> 20:51.033
This is my first time attending, but I know my colleague Jenny Singh has attended in the past.

20:51.533 --> 20:53.994
This is a very targeted forum.

20:54.594 --> 20:57.835
conference for alternative schools, looking at accountability issues.

20:58.535 --> 21:11.000
